editorialNotes.standard: Part digital toy and part planetary handbook, The Earth gives kids insight into the workings of our world in a way thatâs delightfully intuitive and fun. From rockslides to earthquakes to erupting volcanoes, these artful interactive dioramas respond to tapping and swiping with results that are both whimsical and educational.
